title: New: Rochelle Jordan – Here I Go
content:
Photo Credit: Malcolm Gray

As fate would have it, Canadian songstress Rochelle Jordan appeared in our third Sound of 2012 section, only just a few hours ago. So, if you needed any further temptation to check out her music, here it is, in the form of new track Here I Go. Where Drake is too soppily cliched and The Weeknd is too sleazy, Jordan squeezes herself in the middle, hitting the honest and emotional yet sensual and classy nail right on the head. This number appears pretty heavily Beyonce inspired, with the repetitive, slightly wooden beat lending itself to Jordan’s sassy vocals. Check out Here I Go below.
